BHAI rates per 100,000 population (Germany vs EU/EEA)

Source: R/BHAIBYE.R
bhai_rates.Rd

Format

A data frame with columns:

geo

Geography ("Germany", "EU/EEA").

sample

Data source ("German PPS", "ECDC PPS (EU/EEA)").

hai

HAI type: HAP, UTI, BSI, SSI, CDI.

metric

One of "HAIs", "Deaths", "DALYs".

per100k

Rate per 100,000 population.

per100k_low

Lower 95\ per100k_highUpper 95\

Zacher et al. (2019), Eurosurveillance. data(bhai_rates) Population-standardised rates by HAI type and metric (HAIs, Deaths, DALYs) with 95\ datasets
